  "title": "Sales Support (5 days + AWS + VB)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Duties & Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li>Manage and coordinate the promotion and sales activities for the company’s parts and products.</li><li>Conduct market research and analyze industry trends and developments.</li><li>Provide pricing strategy recommendations to regional subsidiaries.</li><li>Liaise with headquarters to ensure up-to-date information on product availability, pricing, and service offerings.</li><li>Prepare, manage, and coordinate customer and dealer quotations for special or custom-made products efficiently.</li><li>Prepare, manage, and issue announcements regarding new products or product changes in a timely and accurate manner.</li><li>Support the sales planning department with general operations to help achieve departmental goals.</li></ul><p></p><h2><strong>Skills and Competencies</strong></h2><ul><li>Preferably holds a NITEC/Diploma in Office Skills or Engineering-related fields.</li><li>Able to perform well in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Strong team player with excellent interpersonal skills.</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates who wish to apply for the above positions, please click \"Apply now\" </p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. </p><p>JAC Recruitment Pte. Ltd. </p><p>EA License No: 90C3026</p><p>EA Personnel No: R23113652</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Yi Lei</p>",
